# Server static media — copyrighted TOEIC materials, do NOT commit to public repo
# Ignore CONTENTS of audio/images so .gitkeep can still track folder structure.
# (Ignoring the directory itself would stop git from descending into it,
# which would hide the .gitkeep negation pattern below.)
server/public/audio/**/*
server/public/images/**/*
!server/public/audio/**/
!server/public/images/**/
!server/public/**/.gitkeep
!server/public/**/README.md

# Raw source PDFs (ETS đề thi gốc — bản quyền, chỉ dùng local để extract content)
# Same pattern as server/public: ignore CONTENTS, allow folders + select .md files
_raw_pdfs/**/*
!_raw_pdfs/**/
!_raw_pdfs/README.md
!_raw_pdfs/**/IMAGE_CHECKLIST.md

# Local dev tools (PlantUML jar ~22MB — script in URL tải khi thiếu file)
tools/